1. Load the workbook.
2. Write the new formula into cell B13 (overwriting the existing one).
3. Save the workbook to the output directory with the same filename.
4. Run `recalculate` to evaluate formulas.
5. Reload the file with `data_only=True` and print the resulting value of B13 to verify it is populated.

